transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haanji.
Executive: Hello good morning sir, mai Malvika baat kar rahi hu.
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Haan dusre number pe baat kariye aap unse.
Executive: Sir wo call pick nahi kar rahe wo na call.
Customer: Abhi wo baat
Executive: Ek minute us number pe mam baat chal rahi hai ji. Abhi kar dete hai baat karata hu ji.
Customer: Accha accha thik hai thik hai mai kar leti hu connect.
Executive: Thik hai ji.
summary:
